getPlugIn

public PlugIn getPlugIn(int plugIn_const)
Returns the specified plugin. To prevent the errors of programers it is highly recomanded to test the returned reference to its particular type before typecasting the result according to the constant which was passed as the argument.

Parameters:
plugIn_const - Identifier of the desired plugin. Particular constants can be found in PlugInsLoader class.
Returns:
PlugIn It is the desired loaded plugIn.
